'''林肯圣经'''是[[美国总统|美国总统]][[亚伯拉罕·林肯|亚伯拉罕·林肯]]所拥有的[[圣经|圣经]]。林肯家族将这本圣经捐赠给[[国会图书馆_(美国)|国会图书馆]]，由后者负责收藏。

== 概述 ==
这本圣经是一部[[牛津大學出版社|牛津大学出版社]]版本[[钦定版圣经|英王钦定版圣经]]，其出版于1853年，有1280页，尺寸大约为{{Convert|6|in}} 长{{Convert|4|in}}宽{{Convert|1.75|in}}厚<ref name="ET">{{cite web|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/ET_Cetera/Obama_first_Prez_to_use_Lincolns_Bible/articleshow/4008813.cms|title=Obama first president to use Lincoln's Bible|date=2009-01-20|publisher=The Economic Times|accessdate=2017-02-01|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204190903/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/ET_Cetera/Obama_first_Prez_to_use_Lincolns_Bible/articleshow/4008813.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>，封套为[[勃艮第酒紅|勃艮第红]][[天鹅绒|天鹅绒]][[贴金|镶金]]边<ref name="LoC">{{cite web|url=http://www.loc.gov/today/pr/2008/08-236.html|title=President-Elect Obama To Take Oath of Office on Lincoln-Inaugural Bible from Library of Congress|date=2008-12-23|publisher=[[Library_of_Congress|Library of Congress]]|accessdate=2017-02-01|archive-date=2012-07-29|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69VeYFB6O?url=http://www.loc.gov/today/pr/2008/08-236.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。圣经的[[扉页|扉页]]背面带有美国最高法院的印章以及{{le|林肯第一次總統就職典禮|First inauguration of Abraham Lincoln|1861年就职典礼}}的纪录。这本圣经并不是罕见的版本，而不具有林肯圣经的历史意义的类似圣经价值约为30[[美元|美元]]或40美元。

== 历史 ==
林肯在1861年3月4日抵达[[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]时，他的行李包括他的圣经，都还没有送达。[[美国最高法院|美国最高法院]]书记官长威廉·托马斯·卡罗尔（William Thomas Carroll）拿出一本供官方使用的圣经。这本圣经后来成为林肯圣经<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/2100-18563_162-4736457.html|title=The Real Story Of The Lincoln Bible|accessdate=2012-08-13|publisher=CBS News|archive-date=2012-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120423231641/http://www.cbsnews.com/2100-18563_162-4736457.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这本圣经由卡罗尔保管了一段时间，而林肯则在一未知时间取得了它。此后，此书一直由林肯家族成员保管。直到1928年，林肯家族的后人[[罗伯特·托德·林肯|罗伯特·托德·林肯]]的[[遗孀|遗孀]]{{le|玛丽·哈兰·林肯|Mary Harlan Lincoln|玛丽·尤尼斯·哈伦}}将其捐赠给美国国会图书馆<ref name="usnews">{{Cite web|url=http://www.usnews.com/news/blogs/god-and-country/2008/12/23/the-story-behind-the-lincoln-bible-at-obamas-inauguration|title=The Story Behind the Lincoln Bible at Obama's Inauguration - God & Country|accessdate=2012-08-13|date=2008-12-23|publisher=usnews.com|archive-date=2020-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200205161621/https://www.usnews.com/news/blogs/god-and-country/2008/12/23/the-story-behind-the-lincoln-bible-at-obamas-inauguration|dead-url=no}}</ref>。圣经被捐赠时，《[[申命记|申命记]]》第31章和《[[何西阿书|何西阿书]]》的第4章中含有注记<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=1XVFAAAAIBAJ&sjid=obwMAAAAIBAJ&pg=958,4959444&dq=lincoln-bible&hl=en|title=Lincoln's Bible Pages Marked: Was it Chance That Left Two Ribbon Markers At Passages? Verses Seen as Appropriate: Bring to Mind Dark Days That Lincoln Passed Through After Taking Office|date=1928-12-02|newspaper=The Telegraph-Herald|accessdate=2013-08-09|deadurl=no|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|page=12|archive-date=2015-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151223193604/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=1XVFAAAAIBAJ&sjid=obwMAAAAIBAJ&pg=958,4959444&dq=lincoln-bible&hl=en}}</ref>。[[巴拉克·奥巴马|巴拉克·奥巴马]]在[[2009年美國總統就職典禮|2009年]]<ref name="MSNBC">{{Cite news|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/28366102/|title=Obama chooses Lincoln's Bible for inauguration|date=2008-12-23|accessdate=2013-08-09|deadurl=no|archive-date=2012-07-29|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69VeXTJrM?url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/28366102/}}</ref>和{{le|2013年美國總統就職典禮|Second inauguration of Barack Obama|2013年}}<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.pjstar.com/news/x127109197/Lincoln-Bible-heightens-symbolism|title=Lincoln Bible heightens symbolism - Peoria, IL|accessdate=2012-08-13|last=Ori|first=Ryan|publisher=pjstar.com|archive-date=2009-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090321133446/http://www.pjstar.com/news/x127109197/Lincoln-Bible-heightens-symbolism|dead-url=no}}</ref>的就职典礼上都使用此书起誓。直到2009年庆祝林肯诞生二百周年，这本圣经都一直在国会图书馆展出。2016年9月14日，[[卡拉·海登|卡拉·海登]]宣誓就任第十四任{{le|美國國會圖書館館長|Librarian of Congress|国会图书馆馆长}}时使用这本圣经<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://blogs.loc.gov/loc/2016/09/welcome-carla-hayden/#comment-1586765|title=Welcome Carla Hayden|date=2016-09-15|publisher=Library of Congress|accessdate=2017-02-01|archive-date=2021-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210320061605/https://blogs.loc.gov/loc/2016/09/welcome-carla-hayden/#comment-1586765|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[唐纳德·特朗普|唐纳德·特朗普]]在2017年1月20日[[2017年美國總統就職典禮|总统就职宣誓]]时也用手按这本圣经以及他童年时的圣经<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2017/01/18/the-symbolism-of-trumps-two-inaugural-bible-choices-from-lincoln-to-his-mother/|title=The symbolism of Trump’s two inaugural Bible choices, from Lincoln to his mother|last=Mettler|first=Katie|date=2017-01-18|newspaper=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|accessdate=2017-02-01|archive-date=2017-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121003555/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2017/01/18/the-symbolism-of-trumps-two-inaugural-bible-choices-from-lincoln-to-his-mother/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

